# auto-rotoscope

Tool for game creators to automate rotoscoping motion-capture video into sprites, using basic silhouette detection. Uses Windows Forms for the front end.

For screeenshots, see:

http://gamedev.sleptlate.org/blog/99-2d-pixel-graphic-motion-capture/

A video of the results of the program, after additional manual editing:

http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=kvUz2-XBPq4